WEBVTT

1
00:00:20.145 --> 00:00:21.812
- What's up. Ghost Rider?
- You good?

2
00:00:21.813 --> 00:00:23.063
{\an8}Never better.

3
00:00:23.064 --> 00:00:24.898
{\an8}OK. kids. bye-bye time.

4
00:00:24.899 --> 00:00:27.109
{\an8}Thanks for the trip
down memory lane.

5
00:00:27.110 --> 00:00:28.527
{\an8}Um. where's Evans?

6
00:00:28.528 --> 00:00:30.779
{\an8}Uh. I think
she's by the family room.

7
00:00:30.780 --> 00:00:32.406
She is.

8
00:00:32.407 --> 00:00:33.907
Hey. hey. hey.
where are you going?

9
00:00:33.908 --> 00:00:35.451
I'm not gonna scan
all this by myself.

10
00:00:35.452 --> 00:00:37.036
Cruz has a question
on my cellulitis.

11
00:00:37.037 --> 00:00:38.621
I'll be right back.
- You better.

12
00:00:38.622 --> 00:00:39.913
- Two minutes tops.
- Where's Mel?

13
00:00:39.914 --> 00:00:41.415
Where's Donnie?

14
00:00:41.416 --> 00:00:42.875
They should be helping you.
- I don't know.

15
00:00:42.876 --> 00:00:44.627
OK. day shift. listen up.

16
00:00:44.628 --> 00:00:46.754
We're doing really well.
but we still got a ways to go.

17
00:00:46.755 --> 00:00:48.839
And nobody's going home
until all these paper charts

18
00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:50.591
are digitized. including me.

19
00:00:50.592 --> 00:00:52.509
And then we're free
to celebrate our freedom?

20
00:00:52.510 --> 00:00:53.636
Exactly.

21
00:00:53.637 --> 00:00:54.845
Well. can you kick some ass

22
00:00:54.846 --> 00:00:56.013
and get the staff to hurry up

23
00:00:56.014 --> 00:00:57.181
on the EHR home pages?

24
00:00:57.182 --> 00:00:58.932
Where are Larry and Antoine?

25
00:00:58.933 --> 00:01:00.225
Antoine's fighting on the phone

26
00:01:00.226 --> 00:01:01.602
with his girlfriend outside.

27
00:01:01.603 --> 00:01:04.396
And Larry's on a cafeteria run.

28
00:01:04.397 --> 00:01:06.940
Yeah. that tracks.

29
00:01:06.941 --> 00:01:09.068
We've got five patients
in beds waiting to be seen.

30
00:01:09.069 --> 00:01:11.070
How do you want to play this...
man to man or zone?

31
00:01:11.071 --> 00:01:12.488
The zone.

32
00:01:12.489 --> 00:01:14.156
Have Cruz and Ellis split up
the new five.

33
00:01:14.157 --> 00:01:15.532
You take North and Central.

34
00:01:15.533 --> 00:01:17.284
I'll take South and Trauma.
- Cool.

35
00:01:17.285 --> 00:01:18.327
Want to switch at 1:00 AM?

36
00:01:18.328 --> 00:01:19.495
Why?

37
00:01:19.496 --> 00:01:20.663
Variety is the spice of life.

38
00:01:20.664 --> 00:01:22.122
I thought that was garlic.

39
00:01:22.123 --> 00:01:25.125
Oh. sorry.

40
00:01:25.126 --> 00:01:27.002
I told you I'd be fast.

41
00:01:27.003 --> 00:01:29.129
OK. let's do this
and get out of here.

42
00:01:29.130 --> 00:01:30.255
What's the hurry?

43
00:01:30.256 --> 00:01:31.507
Got some hay to pitch?

44
00:01:31.508 --> 00:01:32.925
Ha.

45
00:01:34.427 --> 00:01:36.178
Oh. shoot.
- What?

46
00:01:36.179 --> 00:01:38.806
Uh. my ID badge is missing.

47
00:01:38.807 --> 00:01:39.848
- Oh. no.
The one you just got?

48
00:01:39.849 --> 00:01:41.183
How'd you lose it?

49
00:01:41.184 --> 00:01:42.184
- I don't know.
It must have come off.

50
00:01:42.185 --> 00:01:43.519
Classic.

51
00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:44.937
Hope you remember
your login and password.

52
00:01:44.938 --> 00:01:46.063
OK. Retrace your steps.

53
00:01:46.064 --> 00:01:47.523
