54
00:01:47.524 --> 00:01:50.192
Uh. I was with Ogilvie
in the Ambulance Bay.

55
00:01:50.193 --> 00:01:52.361
Not with Colonel Mustard
in the library?

56
00:01:52.362 --> 00:01:54.405
Who's... what?

57
00:01:54.406 --> 00:01:55.699
No.

58
00:01:56.991 --> 00:01:59.369
The boy has no clue.

59
00:02:03.707 --> 00:02:05.791
Please don't do that.

60
00:02:05.792 --> 00:02:07.543
Oh. ma'am. I gotta go.

61
00:02:07.544 --> 00:02:10.255
I sit here any longer.
I'm gonna get bedsores.

62
00:02:12.424 --> 00:02:15.384
I... I'm supposed to get
some CT results.

63
00:02:15.385 --> 00:02:17.845
Any idea how much longer
that's gonna be?

64
00:02:17.846 --> 00:02:20.264
Shouldn't be much longer.

65
00:02:20.265 --> 00:02:22.891
Where's that Nurse Vivi?

66
00:02:22.892 --> 00:02:24.560
You don't want any of that.

67
00:02:24.561 --> 00:02:26.854
- No?
- No. she's out of your league.

68
00:02:26.855 --> 00:02:28.772
What league do you think
I play in?

69
00:02:28.773 --> 00:02:31.567
Uh. old timer's night.

70
00:02:31.568 --> 00:02:33.235
Yeah. you're probably right.

71
00:02:33.236 --> 00:02:36.405
