a veteran presence.

72
00:02:36.406 --> 00:02:38.574
Well. don't say
I didn't warn you.

73
00:02:38.575 --> 00:02:40.367
You are here for your heart.
after all.

74
00:02:40.368 --> 00:02:41.869
My heart's been broken before.

75
00:02:41.870 --> 00:02:43.412
What's one more time?

76
00:02:43.413 --> 00:02:45.497
Uh. she's engaged
to a jujitsu instructor.

77
00:02:45.498 --> 00:02:47.166
With a bang.
not a whimper. baby.

78
00:02:48.585 --> 00:02:50.252
And it's a cool bath
a couple times a day

79
00:02:50.253 --> 00:02:52.796
