137
00:04:54.711 --> 00:04:56.086
Dr. Robby. sorry.

138
00:04:56.087 --> 00:04:57.087
I was just...

139
00:04:57.088 --> 00:04:58.547
One of your TikToks? Yeah.

140
00:04:58.548 --> 00:05:00.173
About those. listen.
I'm not so sure that...

141
00:05:00.174 --> 00:05:02.009
- No. no. I was just sharing...
